prompt.title: Embedding for AI-Powered App Development Simplified
prompt.content: Promptbook is designed to leverage the power of large language models (like GPT or Claude) to transform human-computer interaction. It aims to make AI application development accessible to non-programmers and non-technical people while maintaining the benefits of version control systems.
